│ The board is 9x9 consisting of 3x3 smaller          │                │       │
│ subboards where each cell can be empty (-), contain │                │       │
│ an X, or contain an O. To indicate a move, Use the  │                │       │
│ corresponding number for the cell where you want to │                │       │
