│ Note that a player's move determines where the      │                │       │
│ opponent can move in the next move. For example, if │                │       │
│ player A moves at top-left corner of a subboard,    │                │       │
│ the next player has to move at the top-left         │                │       │
│ subboard. If the board one being sent to, in this   │                │       │
